    the Jenkinsfile (which acts as the orchestrator) and 
    the Project Files (which define the "how-to" for each tool).

    Think of the Jenkinsfile as the Project Manager who says when to do things,
    while the pom.xml or properties files are the Specialists who know how to do them.

